data.description: Gorgeous new construction in gated golf course community and Brock ISD. Flexible floor plan with spacious open concept features 4 bedrooms, study, game room, large living and custom kitchen with huge island workspace. Master suite connects to laundry for added convenience. Upgrades include hand scraped hardwood flooring, custom cabinetry, decorative lighting and stainless appliances. Located on a corner lot with mature trees. Comes with builders 2-10 warranty!
